  "is_free": false,
  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN US ON DISCORD AND TWITTER</h1><p><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://discord.gg/JeFSG4s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  ><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/375530/extras/Discord.png?t=1523385512\" ></a></a><br>Football, Tactics &amp; Glory has its Discord server, where players talk about the game, share their experience, discuss tactics. I often answer questions there and share there work in progress. Join us by <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://discord.gg/JeFSG4s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >this link</a></a>!<br><br><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Creoteam_games\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  ><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/375530/extras/Twitter.png?t=1523385512\" ></a></a><br>Creoteam's <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Creoteam_games\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >twitter account</a></a> is the first place, where we share the game's development progress, fresh screenshots, gifs etc. Subscribe to it, and you will always know our news.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/375530/extras/FT_600_RPG.jpg?t=1523385512\" ><br><strong>Football, Tactics &amp; Glory is a football management game for those who love strategy games. </strong><br><br>Football, Tactics &amp; Glory reinvents the basics of the football management genre, making it appealing to everyone, not only the most hardcore football management aficionados.<br><br>As a result, this game is deep enough to keep many players engrossed for hundreds of hours already. Football, Tactics &amp; Glory skips the boring parts of football management games - all those endless tables, numbers, routine and micromanagement. <br><br>If you enjoy turn-based gameplay, strategy or tycoon games, you will love Football, Tactics &amp; Glory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/375530/extras/FT_600.jpg?t=1523385512\" ><br>- Unique turn-based system<br>- Club development involving economics and RPG elements<br>- Powerful face editor<br>- Mod support which allows you to create real-life leagues<br>- Online game support<br>- Twitch integration (spectators can interact with a streamer)",
  "about_the_game": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/375530/extras/FT_600_RPG.jpg?t=1523385512\" ><br><strong>Football, Tactics &amp; Glory is a football management game for those who love strategy games. </strong><br><br>Football, Tactics &amp; Glory reinvents the basics of the football management genre, making it appealing to everyone, not only the most hardcore football management aficionados.<br><br>As a result, this game is deep enough to keep many players engrossed for hundreds of hours already. Football, Tactics &amp; Glory skips the boring parts of football management games - all those endless tables, numbers, routine and micromanagement. <br><br>If you enjoy turn-based gameplay, strategy or tycoon games, you will love Football, Tactics &amp; Glory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/375530/extras/FT_600.jpg?t=1523385512\" ><br>- Unique turn-based system<br>- Club development involving economics and RPG elements<br>- Powerful face editor<br>- Mod support which allows you to create real-life leagues<br>- Online game support<br>- Twitch integration (spectators can interact with a streamer)",
  "short_description": "Football, Tactics &amp; Glory is using a ball rather than swords and sorcery in turn-based battles, developing a club instead of a castle, and leveling up your units after clashes on the stadium. You will like it if you enjoy any combo of turn-based mechanics, team development, tycoon-style games and football.",
  "supported_languages": "English, Russian, Ukrainian, French, German, Spanish, Czech, Italian, Simplified Chinese",
  "reviews": "\u201cFootball Tactics is the most captivating indie PC game I have played. In addition to the strategic gameplay and management aspects, the fact that games play out quickly helped keep me going \u201cjust one more turn.\u201d In that way, it is very much like bigger strategy titles, like the aforementioned Civilization series. Plus, it is polished and charmingly animated, with easy to read menus and a very helpful tutorial.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.operationsports.com/football-tactics-impressions-steam-early-access/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Operation Sports</a></a><br><br>\u201cThink Heroes of Might and Magic but with footballers instead of griffins...\u201d<br>9/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.thepixelempire.net/football-tactics-pc-review.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >The Pixel Empire</a></a><br><br>\u201cA real innovation:\u00a0deeply addictive\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gamestar.de/artikel/football-tactics-early-access-der-koenigstransfer-fuer-fans-von-fussballmanagern,3321776.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >http://www.gamestar.de/artikel/football-tactics-early-access-der-koenigstransfer-fuer-fans-von-fussballmanagern,3321776.html</a></a><br>",
